{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Face the invading Dark Wisp</h2>Play as the guardian Specter and his flying companion Mip as they travel deep into the depths to seal away the invading evil spirits known as the Dark Wisps, a group of ghostly apparitions who cause harm to the innocent creatures of the forest.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/platformingGif.gif?t=1704851645\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore an interconnected world as you fight your way against hordes of Ghostly Apparitions.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Switch between melee and ranged attacks as Specter and Mip. Slice your enemies as Specter &amp; shoot enemies from a distance as Mip.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get through tricky obstacles using Mip's Echolocation ability to reveal hidden platforms.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock new magic abilities for both Specter and Mip. Blow enemies into the wind with the tornado ability. Summon spectral swords that aid you in combat.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Obtain key items and solve light puzzles.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Inspect items you collected in your inventory.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Face hordes of Ghostly enemies and bosses.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Partial support for gamepad, &amp; mouse + keyboard.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/smallBossGif.gif?t=1704851645\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Need More Power","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2072030/27f938b65ba84325d9009dc73a387ee22a7efda9.jpg"},{"name":"Power Hungry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2072030/10645073532b0e3080b8b6de447335c74592ecc1.jpg"},{"name":"Unstoppable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pu